## Tooltip Boilerplate JSX

Tooltips provide helpful information and can include detailed context about a specific component when a user hovers on it.

### Import

```js
import { Tooltip } from "@vibe/core";
```

### Tooltip on IconButton

```jsx
<Tooltip content="Hidden columns">
    <IconButton kind="secondary" size="small" icon={Hide} />
</Tooltip>
```

### Tooltip with definition

```jsx
<Tooltip content="Item name: Bottom sheets">
    <Button kind="secondary" size="small" leftIcon={Subitems}>
        Subitem
    </Button>
</Tooltip>
```

### Tooltip with no delay

```jsx
<Tooltip immediateShowDelay={0} content="I'm a tooltip">
    <IconButton icon={Menu} kind="secondary" size="small" />
</Tooltip>
```

### Tooltip with 3000ms delay

```jsx
<Tooltip immediateShowDelay={3000} content="I'm a tooltip">
    <IconButton icon={Menu} kind="secondary" size="small" />
</Tooltip>
```